  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA308-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu neñciṉāl poruḷ valikkappaṭṭa talaimakaṉ talaimakaḷai eyti āṟṟāṉāy neñciṟkuc (C1: neñciṉaic; EV: neñciṉiṉ) colli celavu aḻuṅkiyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how HE, who was forced to [pursue] wealth by [his own] heart, dispensed with going, speaking to the heart as one who was unable to bear it when reaching HER.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA308">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            celavirai vuṟṟa varavam pōṟṟi</l>
<l>            malarē ruṇkaṇ paṉivara vāyiḻai</l>
<l>            yāntaṟ karaiyavu nāṇiṉaḷ varuvōḷ</l>
<l>            vēṇṭā maiyiṉ meṉmela vantu</l>
<l>            viṉavalun takaittaluñ cellā ḷāki</l>
<l>            veṟikamaḻ tuṟumuṭi tayaṅka nalviṉaip</l>
<l>            poṟiyaḻi pāvaiyiṟ kalaṅki neṭituniṉain</l>
<l>            tāka maṭaitan tōḷē yatukaṇ</l>
<l>            ṭīrmaṭ ceykai nīrpaṭu pacuṅkalam</l>
<l>            perumaḻaip peyaṟkēṟ ṟāṅkumeṉ</l>
<l>            poruṇmali neñcam puṇarntuvan taṉṟē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Upon noticing the noise produced by the hurry to go,</l>
<l>	even as we call her of choice jewels, while dew comes into</l>
<l>[her] blossom-like collyrium eyes, she would come ashamed.</l>
<l>	Coming slowly slowly, as if not wanting to,</l>   
<l>thinking long, agitated as an image with dissolving form(?)<note place="foot">T.V.G. explains here that the comparison refers to a mechanical doll with broken mechanism (<term xml:lang="ta">poṟi aḻi</term>).</note>,</l>
<l>	well done, while [her] thick hair knot fragrant with perfume glitters,</l>
<l>she sunk down on [my] bosom.</l>
<l>Seing that,</l>
<l>like a fresh pot exposed to the great rains,</l>
<l>absorbing water as wet clay will do,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">ceykai</term> has to be understood here as "characteristic action".</note></l>
<l>[my] soft heart full of wealth came to unite [with her].</l>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="11b">
  <l>[my] soft heart full of wealth rejoiced to unite [with her].</l>
</lg>
      </lg>
      </div>
